# Privacy policy

Webconverger is designed to ensure users privacy and [[security]] whilst
surfing the Web.

Webconverger Ltd does not currently collect any information about how you use
Webconverger.  Earlier versions (before 2.31) were collecting version, boot
parameters (e.g. homepage=) and MAC information.

All *.webconverger.[com|org] sites have standard [Apache](http://apache.org/)
logs, which will log you if you visit that site. Logs are typically rotated
(deleted) within a year.
